# Analyze Zoom Speech SDK Log

## Description
Analyze Zoom Speech SDK logs to identify errors, performance issues, and decode responses.

## Purpose
This command helps developers troubleshoot Zoom Speech SDK integration issues by parsing and analyzing log files.

## Usage
```
analyze_zoom_speech_sdk_log <log_file_path>
```

## Features
- Parse speech SDK log format
- Identify error patterns
- Decode response messages
- Performance metrics analysis
- Timeline reconstruction

## Keywords
speech, sdk, zoom, log, analyze, decode, response, error, debug
